strings.Value: "Why we don't have no fresh meat today?"
"I didn't get it. Why no one is hunting some meat?!"
"No one wants to go hunting. That includes me. You can do it yourself if you wish."
"We have some ration packs stored, Amiri. We shouldn't expose ourselves to risk by wandering here alone."
"Oh, I'd just love some meat! I'd go myself, but I'm no good as a hunter..."
